ACB All these bears never learn The UFC deal has nothing to do with viewership within the sport Sure the viewership with help them get their name seen by others but thats not their goal Its objective is to see how well CBD helps athletes recover from fights and injuries Its a small step in the right direction If they get enough statistical proof that CDB is a better form to alleviate pain and speed up the recovery period for athletes just that alone will thrive their products They can pitch this to bigger leagues such as NFL MLB NBA etc along with the fact that this will not lead to players getting addicted to their products NFL is the main one that comes to mind with so many athletes falling into addiction from prescription drugs that they are given to deal with pain Also maybe just maybe CBD can help with the concussion issue that is a cancer in the sports market Its a win win scenario and one that Im looking forward to the outcome of their research
